---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HeaderScreen from "../../components/HeaderScreen.astro";

---

<BaseLayout title="About NV Flight" description="Safety-first, primacy-driven flight training with mountain expertise.">
  <HeaderScreen data

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 space-y-24">
    <!-- Core Values -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-muted-900">Our Core Values</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-muted-700 max-w-3xl">
        Our culture is built to excel—prioritizing safety, teaching with primacy, and tailoring training to each student’s goals. We specialize in mountain flying and produce confident, capable aviators.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Safety & Decisions</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">Safety drives every briefing, maneuver, and go/no-go decision.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Primacy</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">High value on doing it right the first time—habits formed early last.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Expedited Training</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">Available CFIs and aircraft keep your momentum strong and efficient.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Student-Centered</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">We listen first, then tailor a plan so you get the training you need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-muted-900">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-700">
          <p>
            NV Flight began when our founder moved back home to Reno and purchased a Cherokee. For a time, it was a one-woman show—growing organically with the support of friends and family.
          </p>
          <p>
            Soon after launch, the school became a Part 141 operation. Today, NV Flight is owned by CFIs with deep experience flying in one of the most challenging environments: the mountains.
          </p>
          <p>
            With ~15 years of worldwide flying experience and strong maintenance/mechanical insight, our team delivers training that builds judgment, capability, and confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ol class="relative border-s border-muted-200 ps-6">
          <li class="mb-10 ms-6">
            <span class="absolute -start-3 mt-1 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-muted-900">Humble Beginnings</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-muted-700">Back in Reno with a Cherokee, growing through word of mouth.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-10 ms-6">
            <span class="absolute -start-3 mt-1 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-muted-900">Structure & Standards</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-muted-700">Became a Part 141 school, reinforcing consistency and quality.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="ms-6">
            <span class="absolute -start-3 mt-1 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-muted-900">Expert-Led Growth</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-muted-700">Owned and run by CFIs seasoned in mountain flying.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Training Focus -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-muted-900">How We Train</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Mountain Expertise</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">Endorsements and real-world terrain experience build strong airmanship.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Mechanically Savvy</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">Maintenance perspective informs smarter decisions and safer flying.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-muted-200 bg-white p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted-900">Beyond a Checkride</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted-700">We don’t just teach to fly—we train pilots for a range of objectives.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="rounded-3xl bg-muted-50 p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-muted-900">Ready to start your training?</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-muted-700">
            Get a plan tailored to your goals and timeline—whether that’s a license, a mountain endorsement, or a pro path.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 md:justify-end">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-primary-600 px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white shadow transition hover:bg-primary-700">
            Talk to an Instructor
          </a>
          <a href="/programs" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-muted-300 px-6 py-3 font-medium text-muted-900 transition hover:bg-muted-100">
            See Programs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
